---
import pythonFile from '../assets/python/testo.py?raw';
---

<section id="python" class="py-12 space-y-8 animate-fade-in">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
      <div class="h-1 w-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-utem-blue to-utem-purple"></div>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-utem-blue to-utem-purple">Proyectos Python</p>
    </span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-utem-dark">Innovación aplicada: chatbots, visión y ciencia de datos</h2>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-utem-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Selección de proyectos universitarios desarrollados por estudiantes ICCD para mostrar el potencial de la carrera:
      IA conversacional, visión por computador y analítica avanzada. El antiguo prototipo en Streamlit queda solo como
      referencia descargable.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
    <!-- Tarjeta principal -->
    <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-utem-gray/50 bg-gradient-card p-8 space-y-6 shadow-subtle hover:shadow-glow hover:border-utem-blue/30 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-utem-blue to-utem-purple flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Py</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-utem-blue">Proyectos destacados</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-utem-dark/80">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-blue mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span><strong class="text-utem-dark">Chatbot académico:</strong> FAQ de la carrera con intents entrenados en materiales UTEM.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-purple mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span><strong class="text-utem-dark">Reconocimiento facial:</strong> prototipo de control de acceso para laboratorios y eventos.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-blue mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span><strong class="text-utem-dark">Visualización 3D:</strong> superficies y gráficos interactivos para divulgación técnica.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-purple mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span><strong class="text-utem-dark">Dashboard de avisos y recursos:</strong> agenda, links a Drive y contactos oficiales.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-6">
        <a
          href="/downloads/python-code.zip"
          class="group relative rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-utem-blue to-utem-purple px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-glow hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          download
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">Descargar código heredado</span>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-utem-purple to-utem-blue opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/python-info"
          class="group rounded-full border-2 border-utem-gray px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-utem-dark hover:border-utem-blue hover:text-utem-blue hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Ver documentación
          <span class="ml-2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all duration-300">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tarjetas laterales -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="group rounded-xl border border-utem-gray/50 bg-white p-6 shadow-subtle hover:shadow-md hover:border-utem-blue/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-blue"></div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-utem-blue">Propósito</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-utem-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
          Mostrar proyectos concretos que impulsan la carrera: IA, visión y ciencia de datos aplicados a la comunidad.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group rounded-xl border border-utem-gray/50 bg-white p-6 shadow-subtle hover:shadow-md hover:border-utem-purple/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-purple"></div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-utem-purple">Stack sugerido</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="text-sm text-utem-dark/80 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-blue/70"></div>
            <span>Chatbots: Python, FastAPI, Rasa u OpenAI API.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-purple/70"></div>
            <span>Visión: OpenCV, MediaPipe, modelos preentrenados.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-blue/70"></div>
            <span>Gráficos: Plotly, Matplotlib, NumPy.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group rounded-xl border border-utem-gray/50 bg-white p-6 shadow-subtle hover:shadow-md hover:border-utem-teal/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-utem-teal"></div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-utem-teal">Casos de uso</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="text-sm text-utem-dark/80 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-teal/70"></div>
            <span>Orientación a estudiantes y postulantes.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-teal/70"></div>
            <span>Demostraciones para clases y ferias tecnológicas.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-teal/70"></div>
            <span>Prototipos de control de acceso y eventos.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-utem-teal/70"></div>
            <span>Divulgación técnica de la carrera ICCD.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


</section>

<style>
  .bg-gradient-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F8FAFC 50%, #F0F9FF 100%);
  }
</style>